---
title: Fajita-Spiced Pork Chops with Zesty Black Bean Salad & Potato Wedges
description: Bold Tex-Mex flavors pump up tender pork chops with a smoky, slightly spicy kick. You'll whip up crispy roasted potato wedges and a zesty black bean salad with bell pepper, tomato, and scallions to complete this colorful meal that's packed with flavor and ready on the table in a speedy 20 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67cebba86a498293bec85b1a-c815e126.jpeg
